<section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;flip-card-wc&gt;</code> component creates an accessible card that flips between a front and back face. It manages the <code>inert</code> attribute on the hidden face so screen readers only announce visible content.</p>

    <browser-window
